<%# Header %>
<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://picsum.photos/1366/400);">
  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8">
    <h1>SavvyGranny</h1>
    <p>Your parentsâ€™ personal tech support.</p>
    <%= form_for Booking.new do |f| %>
      First name: <%= f.text_field :first_name %><br />
      Last name : <%= f.text_field :last_name %><br />
      Biography : <%= f.text_area :biography %><br />
      Admin?    : <%= f.check_box :admin %><br />
      <%= f.submit %>
    <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# Content %>
<div class="container mt-5">
<div class="h1 text-center">It's simple to be savvy!</div>
<div class="h5 text-center mb-3">Let's say your mom or dad needs help with a tech related task... 
for the tenth time. Now what?</div>
<div class="container d-flex p-0 flex-wrap">
  <div class="card col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 border-0" style="width: 18rem;">
    <div class="card-pic display-3 text-center">
    <i class="fas fa-question"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body text-center d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
      <div class="card-title h5">1. Book a tutor<br></div>
      <p class="card-text">Pick a task and a time - it takes seconds!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 border-0" style="width: 18rem;">
    <div class="card-pic display-3 text-center">
    <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body text-center d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
      <div class="card-title h5">2. Get your parent connected</div>
      <p class="card-text">Just send them a link - no downloads needed.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 border-0" style="width: 18rem;">
    <div class="card-pic display-3 text-center">
    <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body text-center d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
      <div class="card-title h5">3. Stand by (or chill out!)</div>
      <p class="card-text">Our friendly tutors will walk your parent through the task.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 border-0" style="width: 18rem;">
    <div class="card-pic display-3 text-center">
    <i class="far fa-laugh-beam"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body text-center d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
      <div class="card-title h5">4. All done!</div>
      <p class="card-text">Your mom or dad is now savvier than ever! Great job!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

